<HL>
   Marketing &amp; Media:
   Suit by Turner
   Broadcasting Seeks
   Cuba-Sale Rights
   ----
   By Daniel Pearl
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
10/15/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B9
</SO>
<CO>
   TBSA TBSB
</CO>
